metaforRCode.rawtext:
fit <- rma.mv(
	yi = JaspColumn_24_Encoded,
	V = JaspColumn_45_Encoded^2,
	data = dataset,
	random = list(
		'Component 1' = ~1 | JaspColumn_17_Encoded/JaspColumn_20_Encoded
		'Component 2' = ~JaspColumn_23_Encoded | constant),
	struct = c('Component 2' = 'SPGAU'),
	dist = list(JaspColumn_23_Encoded = 'JaspColumn_23_Encoded Distance Matrix'),
	method = 'REML',
	test = 't',
	level = 95,
	control = list(rho.init = 10)
)
